<li>Wollheim, Richard, 1973, &ldquo;Imagination and
Identification&rdquo;, in <em>On Art and the Mind</em>, London: Allen
Land, pp. 54&ndash;83.</li>

<li>Xhignesse, Michel-Antoine, 2021, &ldquo;Imagining Fictional
Contradictions&rdquo;, <em>Synthese</em>, 199: 3169&ndash;3188.
doi:10.1007/s11229-020-02929-0</li>

<li>Yablo, Stephen, 1993, &ldquo;Is Conceivability a Guide to
Possibility?&rdquo; <em>Philosophy and Phenomenological Research</em>,
53(1): 1&ndash;42. doi:10.2307/2108052</li>
</ul>
</div> 

